## 4. Primary Brand Colors

### 4.1 OPRMT Navy

```text
Hex: #071A2F
```

Recommended for:

- Main website sections
- PDF covers
- Documentation headers
- GitHub visual assets
- Presentation title slides
- Footer backgrounds
- Authority strips

Usage note:

Use white or soft white text on OPRMT Navy for accessibility and contrast.

---

### 4.2 Deep System Blue

```text
Hex: #0B2545
```

Recommended for:

- Secondary dark sections
- Card backgrounds
- Diagram panels
- Code-related visual blocks
- Technical callout sections

Usage note:

This color should support the primary navy, not replace it as the main brand anchor.

---

### 4.3 Framework Gold

```text
Hex: #D6A84F
```

Recommended for:

- Accent borders
- Section dividers
- Buttons
- Badges
- Highlight text
- Icons
- Certification accents
- Premium product indicators

Usage note:

Use gold as an accent only. Do not use it as a large background unless contrast is verified.

