## 6. Status and Interface Colors

Use status colors carefully in documentation, dashboards, scorecards, and workflow files.

| Status | Hex | Use |
|---|---:|---|
| Success Green | `#16A34A` | Approved, passed, valid |
| Warning Amber | `#F59E0B` | Needs review, caution, incomplete |
| Error Red | `#DC2626` | Failed, blocked, critical issue |
| Info Blue | `#2563EB` | Notes, references, informational callouts |
| Review Purple | `#7C3AED` | Review, draft, governance check |

Status colors should not replace the core OPRMT™ color system.

