## 9. GitHub Documentation Usage

Markdown files should remain simple and readable. Since GitHub Markdown does not support full visual styling by default, color usage is mostly relevant for:

- Diagrams
- Badges
- Images
- SVG assets
- Documentation covers
- PDF exports
- Presentation exports
- Website embeds
- Product images

Do not force excessive inline HTML styling into Markdown unless there is a clear need.

